All champions with Stealth, all are hated. They&#039;are also all Assassins. No one besides the people that play these champions like to fight these guys. Stealth is a &quot;Fun&quot; mechanic only for the ones using it, to the rest of us we fucking hate it because it&#039;s only on Assassins with Insta-burst. When was the last time you&#039;ve seen a Tank with Stealth? Perma-Stealth in particular is especially cancerous. Evelynn is the only one (That I know of) that has it and she has 100-0 potential. Yes, she has counterplay, like the massive ass range on her W makes people want to use it before they&#039;re in range to follow up, and the fact she&#039;s made of tissue paper, but still. It&#039;s a seriously bullshit mechanic, she only comes out of stealth once you&#039;re 2s charmed and basically dead before you can react.

b4 anyone asks, no, this is not my first account and no I'm not new.
